Ancient Sports: Organized athletic competitions in ancient civilizations.
Medieval Sports: Jousting, archery, and other combat-oriented activities.
Modern Sports: Increased organization, standardization, and professionalism.
Rise of Spectator Sports: Larger audiences, media coverage, and commercialization.
Globalization of Sports: International competitions and cultural exchange.
